# Vendored skill runtimes are build artifacts — rebuilt via each skill's
# scripts/build.sh (webcrack node_modules incl. isolated-vm native addons;
# pure-python decompiler site dirs). Source (skill.json, SKILL.md, runtime/*.py,
# run.mjs, package.json, package-lock.json, build.sh, *.version) is tracked.
skills/*/runtime/node_modules/
skills/*/runtime/site/
